OL,5, Patients who were filmed being         
OL,6, mistreated at an NHS mental health unit
OL,7, were denied "basic dignity and their   
OL,8, human rights", a review has found.     
OL,10,FA BBC Panorama investigation found a   
OL,11,F"toxic culture of humiliation, verbal  
OL,12,Fabuse and bullying" at the Edenfield   
OL,13,FCentre in Prestwich near Manchester.   
OL,15,FSome staff members were sacked or      
OL,16,Fsuspended following the 2022 broadcast.
OL,18,FGreater Manchester Mental Health Trust 
OL,19,F(GMMH) said it was "truly sorry" and   
OL,20,Fcommitted to a "much-improved future". 
